    "name": "Watch Where You're Going",
    "steam_appid": 3291470,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever been so distracted by your phone that you walked into a pole?  <br>If you haven't, this game is for you.<br>If you have, this game is definitely for you!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Watch Where You're Going</strong> - a game about not watching where you're going</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/d8a9f0ab3eee4d7a1ac19a004431104e.poster.avif?t=1766074300\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/d8a9f0ab3eee4d7a1ac19a004431104e.webm?t=1766074300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/d8a9f0ab3eee4d7a1ac19a004431104e.mp4?t=1766074300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stay one step ahead of your inbox</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will constantly receive messages asking you questions. Stay on top of them before your inbox is full.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/f76784e705fc1d8963190094ad88cf6a.webp?t=1766074300\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/f76784e705fc1d8963190094ad88cf6a.poster.avif?t=1766074300\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=450 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >There's an app for everything</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Answers to the questions are scattered across the various apps on the phone. Sometimes it's as simple as looking up the weather. And sometimes you have to work out exactly where to look, or cross-reference multiple apps, or play a minigame. And the timers are ticking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/b04c7e2da91444c5cb488f9ac208e187.poster.avif?t=1766074300\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/b04c7e2da91444c5cb488f9ac208e187.webm?t=1766074300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master different phones</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just when you think you have it all figured out, try playing on completely different phones with completely different gameplay. One phone might have better navigation, but slow animations. Another might be more compact, but harder to type on. Learn all the tricks and nuances to use each one most efficiently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/7da51d1c79b561067c89719c8a6a7822.poster.avif?t=1766074300\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/7da51d1c79b561067c89719c8a6a7822.webm?t=1766074300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play at your own pace</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You won't just get thrown into the fire - climb through multiple difficulty levels as you master the game. Play practice minigames in between runs. Track your stats and high scores all the way through.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >But most importantly, don't forget to <strong>Watch Where You're Going</strong>!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291470/extras/31dbc5a73c2f86f24426535a6711c196.avif?t=1766074300\" width=602 height=600 /></span></p>",
